---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro'
import Header from '../components/Header.astro'
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro'
---

<Layout
  title="About — Crema"
  description="Crema is a Madrid coffee & lifestyle blog by Guillermo Trigo."
>
  <Header slot="header" />

  <section class="about-hero">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="page-label">The blog</div>
      <h1 class="page-title">About Crema</h1>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container about-layout">

      <div class="about-intro">
        <div class="cup-illustration" aria-hidden="true">☕</div>
      </div>

      <div class="about-text prose">
        <h2>Madrid through a coffee cup</h2>

        <p>
          Crema started as a personal spreadsheet of coffee shops I'd visited in Madrid — ratings,
          notes, vibes. At some point the spreadsheet felt insufficient. Good places deserve better
          than a row in a table.
        </p>

        <p>
          So here we are. Crema is an honest record of Madrid's coffee scene: the specialty roasters
          changing the city's palate, the old-school bares where a cortado costs €1.20 and comes
          with a pastry, and everything in between.
        </p>

        <p>
          The rating is out of 10 and it means something. A 7 is good. A 9 is exceptional.
          I don't inflate scores out of politeness.
        </p>

        <h2>About me</h2>

        <p>
          I'm <strong>Guillermo Trigo</strong>, a software engineer based in Madrid.
          I drink too much coffee and walk too many kilometres between café visits.
          I have opinions about espresso extraction ratios and I'm not sorry about that.
        </p>

        <p>
          The Style section is where I write about everything else Madrid offers —
          culture, architecture, neighbourhoods, the stuff you notice when you spend
          hours sitting in coffee shops looking out the window.
        </p>

        <h2>What the ratings mean</h2>

        <div class="rating-guide">
          <div class="rating-row"><span class="r-score r-9">9–10</span><span>Exceptional. Go out of your way.</span></div>
          <div class="rating-row"><span class="r-score r-7">7–8</span><span>Good. Worth a detour.</span></div>
          <div class="rating-row"><span class="r-score r-5">5–6</span><span>Fine. Nothing special.</span></div>
          <div class="rating-row"><span class="r-score r-3">1–4</span><span>Disappointing. Skip it.</span></div>
        </div>

        <p>
          I pay for everything myself. No sponsored visits, no affiliate links.
          Just honest opinions and too much caffeine.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <Footer slot="footer" />
</Layout>

<style>
  .about-hero {
    background: var(--milk);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
    padding: clamp(2.5rem, 6vw, 4rem) 0 clamp(1.5rem, 4vw, 2.5rem);
  }

  .page-label {
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.2em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--caramel);
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .page-title {
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 3.5rem);
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    color: var(--espresso);
  }

  .about-layout {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 180px 1fr;
    gap: 3rem;
    align-items: start;
  }

  .about-intro {
    position: sticky;
    top: 80px;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .cup-illustration {
    font-size: 6rem;
    display: block;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    filter: drop-shadow(0 4px 8px rgba(44,24,16,0.15));
  }

  .about-text {
    max-width: 620px;
  }

  /* Rating guide */
  .rating-guide {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    margin: 1.5rem 0;
    padding: 1.25rem;
    background: var(--milk);
    border-radius: 10px;
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
  }

  .rating-row {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 1rem;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
  }

  .r-score {
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    padding: 2px 10px;
    border-radius: 6px;
    min-width: 50px;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .r-9 { background: #E8F5E9; color: #1A5C2A; border: 1px solid #A5D6A7; }
  .r-7 { background: #FFF8E1; color: #C8860A; border: 1px solid #FFE082; }
  .r-5 { background: #FFF3E0; color: #9A6B00; border: 1px solid #FFCC80; }
  .r-3 { background: #FDECEA; color: #8B2020; border: 1px solid #EF9A9A; }

  @media (max-width: 640px) {
    .about-layout {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .about-intro {
      position: static;
      text-align: left;
    }

    .cup-illustration { font-size: 4rem; }
  }
</style>
